1 for the payment of debt service on revenue bonds issued for the purposes
2 set forth in subsection (a). Subject to any restrictions imposed by
3 appropriation acts, the state board of regents is also authorized to pledge
4 any funds appropriated to it from the Kansas educational building fund or
5 from any other source and transferred to a special revenue fund of the state
6 board of regents specified by statute as a priority for the payment of debt
